{"tid":1690534,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"要由今日既狀態去到全民勇武，中間差D野","createTime":"2019-11-03T11:02:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T17:27:18.000Z","uid":190579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"63f2e5bf092fdec5f1b97a9c1b18b8de293a5b8c","tid":1690534,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T11:02:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">就<ins>唔係</ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跳出連登</span></strong>既<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>勇武向文宣</strong></span></div></span><br />\n<br />\n日撚日見到連登成堆打狗post <br />\n話咩打狗，反衝鋒，全民天台水魔法<br />\n又屌尻和理非行行企企<br />\n又屌尻阻膠阻撚住哂<br />\n<ins>好彩</ins>呢D Message我從來<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">冇喺連儂場見過</span></strong><br />\n<ins>我反暴力咖嘛</ins><br />\n<br />\n有冇諗過連登只係小眾<br />\n老一輩唔會睇<br />\n打工仔冇時間追post<br />\n先會出現咩「由六月講到而家」既困局<br />\n<br />\n現有既連儂場文宣，仍然停留喺「Why」既階段，講緊「點解要出去」<br />\n<br />\n呢類文宣其實已經完成歷史任務<br />\n<br />\n文宣<ins>唔應該</ins>進一步去到「How」，講「要做咩」、「點幫手」<br />\n<br />\n而文宣呢家嘢<br />\n從來係最缺人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6jAQut7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6jAQut7.jpg&h=12d778b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔使望第二個</span></span></strong><br />\n係所有人都應該做，唔使畫到好靚，出到個Message就得<br />\n一張A4一隻大字咁貼出嚟已經夠"},{"pid":"0fdc1e2e2a3d043ad46952fd4996d978c77a7c17","tid":1690534,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T11:04:44.000Z","msg":"我唔想見到呢D暴力信息<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ewXvuvJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FewXvuvJ.png&h=e0beb9ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2964107673602745&amp;id=1799974313349426\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2964107673602745%26id%3D1799974313349426&d=AnzAv